  "verification_notes": "Mike Young completed his 7th season as head coach. Hokies finished 19-13 (8-10 ACC). NOTE: Wikipedia summary listed final overall as 19-13 in one place and 13-18 in another; cross-reference shows 19-13 cited more frequently for the season-end mark. The team preemptively declined an NIT bid citing injuries; did NOT make NCAA Tournament. Athletic director Whit Babcock announced on April 23, 2026 he will step down effective June 30, 2026 (transitioning to AD emeritus role); Babcock is still AD as of 2026-05-21 with no successor publicly named. Mike Young's overall career record and his career record at Virginia Tech specifically not verified — left null. Roster shown is 2025-26 season-end. 2026-27 schedule TBD. Mason Young (head coach's son association) — Owen Odom is at Virginia; Mike Young of Virginia Tech is unrelated.",
